75
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:54,520
My companions' blood,

76
00:06:55,840 --> 00:06:57,400
my savior's blood,

77
00:06:58,920 --> 00:07:01,000
and blood of innocents.

78
00:07:14,880 --> 00:07:16,200
Why am I

79
