who can do this.

83
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:07,560
Only I

84
00:08:09,080 --> 00:08:11,360
can clear the Wang family's reputation.

85
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:13,720
Only I

86
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:16,560
can let the eunuch's faction

87
00:08:16,760 --> 00:08:18,080
