113
00:09:54,520 --> 00:09:55,600
Zening.

114
00:10:02,040 --> 00:10:03,240
Zening?

115
00:10:05,640 --> 00:10:06,920
Li Zening?

116
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:24,520
Uncle.

117
00:10:25,280 --> 00:10:27,920
