119
00:10:37,560 --> 00:10:39,000
What kind of facial expression is that?

120
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:39,840
What's the matter?

121
00:10:44,800 --> 00:10:45,760
It seems like His Majesty

122
00:10:46,640 --> 00:10:47,920
